data.description: VA LOAN ASSUMPTION AVAILABLE. Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom 2-bathroom condo on the second floor, perfectly positioned for comfort and convenience. Experience the joy of moving into a home that's not just a living space but a haven of comfort from day one. Located on the second floor, bask in the natural light that gracefully fills each room, creating an inviting ambiance. Move-in with ease and savor the immediate enjoyment of a kitchen featuring newer appliances. The spacious bedrooms offer a serene retreat, while 2-designated parking ensures stress-free arrivals. With nearby shopping and dining options, this location caters to every lifestyle. Ready to become your sanctuary, this move-in-ready gem awaits. Schedule a showing today!
